<body>
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>
  <div style="height:32px;"></div>
  <main class="legal-main">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use NomadProHub.</p>
    <h2>Who Is Considered a User?</h2>
    <p>For NomadProHub, the only registered user is the site admin or owner. All other visitors access the site for public viewing and do not create accounts or profiles.</p>
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Admin account and profile information</li>
      <li>Usage data and analytics (for all visitors)</li>
      <li>Cookies and tracking technologies</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To provide and improve our services</li>
      <li>To communicate with you</li>
      <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Access, update, or delete your data</li>
      <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
      <li>Request data portability</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Affiliate Marketing & Google AdSense</h2>
    <p>NomadProHub participates in affiliate marketing programs and uses Google AdSense to display ads. This means we may earn commissions from qualifying purchases and display targeted advertisements based on your browsing activity.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Affiliate links may appear in articles and resources.</li>
      <li>Google AdSense uses cookies to serve ads relevant to you.</li>
      <li>We do not share personally identifiable information with advertisers.</li>
      <li>You can manage your ad preferences via Google settings.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For more details or requests, contact us at support@nomadprohub.com.</p>
  </main>
  <div style="height:32px;"></div>
  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
